STATE of Iowa, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Greg Mitchell REDDEN, Defendant-Appellant. No. 18-0876 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed January 9, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

Greg Redden appeals after pleading guilty to operating while intoxicated, assault on a peace officer, and second-degree criminal mischief. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
